text: Nizhneibrayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Yasherganovsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 287 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 36 km from Sterlibashevo, 3 km from Yasherganovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Nizhneibrayevo
